a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6107684\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6107684\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lsq1707829945129.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lsq1707829945129.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lsq1707829945129.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bxj1665702636828\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ProcScript Labels\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__procscript_labels_50619\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A label allows you to name a line of ProcScript. This line can then be branched to with a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">goto</span> statement.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__p_d15152e1_d15153e1_d15154e1\">The format for a label is:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__p_d15155e1_d15156e1_d15157e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcLabel</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__p_d15158e1_d15159e1_d15160e1\">where <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcLabel</var> is the literal name of the label, which can be a maximum of 128 characters.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__note_w2785ab1b5b9_w2786ab1b5_w2787ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Your ProcScript will be more\n         structured if you avoid using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">goto</span> statements and use the\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">while</span> statements instead.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__section_l3x_1kq_k1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d985226e87\">Example: goto ProcScript Label</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__p_d15164e1_d15165e1_d15166e1\">The following example deletes the first 1001 records,\n            then exits the current component. This is typically used when a component is defined for\n            transaction processing.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bxj1665702636828__pre_ryf_dkq_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec \n$1 = 0\nretrieve\nstart: ; the label ends with a colon (:)\nif ($1 = 1001)\n store\n exit\nelse\n remocc\n $1 = $1 + 1\nendif\ngoto start ; but no colon is used in the goto line\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6107684\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6107684\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ProcScript Labels Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ProcScript Labels A label allows you to name a line of ProcScript. This line can then be branched to with a goto statement. The format for a label is: ProcLabel : where ProcLabel is the literal name of the label, which can be a maximum of 128 characters. Note: Your ProcScript will be more structured if you avoid using goto statements and use the repeat and while statements instead. Example: goto ProcScript Label The following example deletes the first 1001 records, then exits the current component. This is typically used when a component is defined for transaction processing. operation exec $1 = 0 retrieve start: ; the label ends with a colon (:) if ($1 = 1001) store exit else remocc $1 = $1 + 1 endif goto start ; but no colon is used in the goto line end; exec Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}